<item>
 <title>Semantic Radar for Firefox</title>
 <link>http://sioc-project.org/firefox</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;Semantic Radar is a semantic metadata detector for Mozilla Firefox.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;!--break--&gt;&lt;!--break--&gt;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;
&lt;!--
function installExtension(anEvent, extensionName, iconURL) {
  var params = new Object();
  params[extensionName] =
           {
               URL: anEvent.target.href,
               IconURL: iconURL,
               toString: function () { return this.URL; }
           };

  var res = InstallTrigger.install(params);
  if (!res) {
       alert(&quot;If you see an error bar appear at the top of your browser, follow these instructions:\n\n&quot; +
               &quot;1. Click the \&quot;Edit Options...\&quot; button on the error bar.\n&quot; +
               &quot;2. Click the \&quot;Allow\&quot; button in the dialog box that appears.\n&quot; +
               &quot;3. Click \&quot;OK\&quot; to confirm and close the dialog box.\n\n&quot; +
               &quot;Now you can install extensions from this site.\n&quot; +
               &quot;Click the \&quot;Install Semantic Radar\&quot; link again to install the extension.&quot;
               );
  }

  return false;
// a href=&quot;http://rdfs.org/semradar/semradar.xpi&quot; onclick=&quot;return installExtension(event, &#039;Semantic Radar&#039;, &#039;http://www.w3.org/RDF/icons/rdf_flyer.48&#039;);&quot;
}
--&gt;&lt;!--
function installExtension(anEvent, extensionName, iconURL) {
  var params = new Object();
  params[extensionName] =
           {
               URL: anEvent.target.href,
               IconURL: iconURL,
               toString: function () { return this.URL; }
           };

  var res = InstallTrigger.install(params);
  if (!res) {
       alert(&quot;If you see an error bar appear at the top of your browser, follow these instructions:\n\n&quot; +
               &quot;1. Click the \&quot;Edit Options...\&quot; button on the error bar.\n&quot; +
               &quot;2. Click the \&quot;Allow\&quot; button in the dialog box that appears.\n&quot; +
               &quot;3. Click \&quot;OK\&quot; to confirm and close the dialog box.\n\n&quot; +
               &quot;Now you can install extensions from this site.\n&quot; +
               &quot;Click the \&quot;Install Semantic Radar\&quot; link again to install the extension.&quot;
               );
  }

  return false;
// a href=&quot;http://rdfs.org/semradar/semradar.xpi&quot; onclick=&quot;return installExtension(event, &#039;Semantic Radar&#039;, &#039;http://www.w3.org/RDF/icons/rdf_flyer.48&#039;);&quot;
}
--&gt;
&lt;/script&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/downloads/latest/3886/addon-3886-latest.xpi&quot;&gt;Install Semantic Radar&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Available &lt;a href=&quot;https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/3886&quot;&gt;at Mozilla Add-ons site&lt;/a&gt;. It is a browser extension which inspects web pages for links to Semantic Web metadata and informs about presence of it by showing an icon in browser&#039;s status bar. Currently it supports &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/rdf-syntax-grammar/#section-rdf-in-HTML&quot;&gt;RDF autodiscovery&lt;/a&gt; (SIOC, FOAF, DOAP and any type) and RDFa metadata detection.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;New: Semantic Radar can now ping the &lt;a href=&quot;http://pingthesemanticweb.com&quot; title=&quot;Semantic Web Ping Service&quot;&gt;Semantic Web Ping Service&lt;/a&gt; when metadata are detected. This allows for a community based discovery of the Semantic Web data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Written by &lt;a href=&quot;http://captsolo.net/info/&quot; title=&quot;Uldis Bojārs - CaptSolo Weblog&quot;&gt;Uldis Bojārs&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.wikier.org/&quot; title=&quot;Sergio Fernández, aka Wikier&quot;&gt;Sergio Fernández&lt;/a&gt;. If you have comments or bug reports please write to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://groups.google.com/group/sioc-dev&quot; title=&quot;SIOC Development mailing list&quot;&gt;SIOC-Dev mailing list&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://captsolo.net/semweb/foaf-captsolo.rdf&quot; type=&quot;application/rdf+xml&quot; title=&quot;FOAF&quot;&gt;...&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
